{
  "stem": "15174.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the Second World War broke out on September 1, 1939, when Germany invaded Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And a couple, or three days later, England and France declared war on Germany because they had this treaty with Poland.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So there was war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the war-- there was no active war on the Western border of Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were invading Poland.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- and they-- just before that, apparently, an agreement had been made with Russia that Germany would take half of Poland, Russia the other half.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Anyway, the-- the Germans overwhelmed Poland pretty rapidly and, unfortunately, that included all my relatives who were-- who were in Poland.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were in the part of Poland that was nearest Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were near Krakow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And-- but it-- as it turned out, it didn't really make any difference where in Poland you were.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You were at great risk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- we-- the war was going on, but we were in Belgium.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Belgium was neutral.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was not at war so we felt fairly safe.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "However, on May 10 of 1940-- almost a year after we got to Belgium-- the Germans attacked France.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they attacked France directly by trying to invade France, but also through Holland and Belgium.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Didn't matter that those two latter countries were neutral.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Germans didn't care.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think they did the same thing in the First World War, too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, they attacked through Belgium and Holland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were in Brussels and I remember, you know, the-- the air raid sirens would sound.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember one time, we had been visiting some friends and we were walking back to our room when the air siren found-- sounded.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was no air raid shelter around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't even know if they had air raid shelters in Belgium.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
